team2869.bethpage.robotics.aerialassist

Class RobotMap

  • java.lang.Object
    • team2869.bethpage.robotics.aerialassist.RobotMap

  • public class RobotMap
extends Object
    The RobotMap is a mapping from the ports sensors and actuators are wired into to a variable name. This provides flexibility changing wiring and also makes checking the wiring easier.
